GLOBAL_LATENCY_DESCRIPTION: change GLOBAL_LATENCY to your lowest usual ping
AA_RATIO_DESCRIPTION: Auto attack glitch emulator. Default is 1, setting it higher increases AA speed.
BH_ANTI_GHOST_DESCRIPTION: Slows down first hit of BH but will stop most ghosting for BH. Activate this if you experience ghosting.
BH_ALGORITHM_2_DESCRIPTION: For people who have bugged BH on algorithm 1 (unstable net), however this algorithm is SLOWER by 10~20ms. BH_ANTI_GHOST is not required for this algorithm.
DISABLE_IFRAME_EMULATION_DESCRIPTION: Will disable emulation for shadow jump and 1k cut, but why?
DISABLE_1K_EMULATION_DESCRIPTION: Will disable emulation for 1k cut, but why?
CHAKRA_QUICK_ATTACK_DESCRIPTION: Auto quick attack after chakra thrust. Requires robotjs.
QUICK_ATTACK_KEY_DESCRIPTION: Quick Attack key, find keyboard syntax list here http://robotjs.io/docs/syntax.
INNER_HARMONY_AUTO_DESCRIPTION: If enabled, will use the X_KEY, Y_KEY, Z_KEY when Inner Harmony is triggered.
X_KEY_DESCRIPTION: X key, find keyboard syntax list here http://robotjs.io/docs/syntax.
Y_KEY_DESCRIPTION: Y key, find keyboard syntax list here http://robotjs.io/docs/syntax.
Z_KEY_DESCRIPTION: Z key, find keyboard syntax list here http://robotjs.io/docs/syntax.
